HEADWORD: Rimey
<hw>Rim"ey</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Cf. OF.
<ets>rimoier</ets>. See <er>Ryime</er>.]</ety> <def>To compose in rhyme;
to versify.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>[Lays] <qex>rimeyed</qex> in their first Breton tongue.</q>
